sentence: In early trading on Tuesday, shares of UnitedHealth Group ( UNH ) topped the list of the day's best performing Dow Jones Industrial Average components, trading up 1.9%.
Year to date, UnitedHealth Group registers a 30.6% gain.
And the worst performing Dow component thus far on the day is Home Depot ( HD ), trading down 1.2%.
Home Depot is showing a gain of 17.6% looking at the year to date performance.
Two other components making moves today are AT&T ( T ), trading down 0.6%, and General Electric ( GE ), trading up 0.6% on the day.
